snippet.textDisplay: During the blizzard of a critical election, candidates may pronounce certain words or cite any historical document as part of their own strategies, although some judicious restraint is very much desirable.  It is true that pulling in the  memories of the established leaders of many years ago who are now deceased and unable to rebut any charges against them, should not be drawn in or besmirched, except the weakness of their policies.  May their souls rest in peace!  Rajiv Gandhi is not a contender in this election. I wish, Modiji abstained from it.  But his flare up is eminently understandable. Mr. Rahul Gandhi has been systematically attacking Mr. Modi personally with so much hate and raw insults, that has long surpassed the limits of legality and common decency.  There is no justification anywhere to brand Mr. Modi as a 'chor' (thief). Rahul has no proof for it, nor any rationale to villify him in the middle of the widespread public of India. Rahul is neither the police, nor the judge.  He has been shouting slogans and instigating his thousands of followers in the audience at big rallies to slander Mr. Modi with this kind of calumny.  This is an unforgivable, unmitigated crime against a person. Rahul is so stupid that he has revived the old slogan raised against his father by the late V.P. Singh who betrayed Rajiv Gandhi and displaced him from the PM's chair, alleging, "Gulli gulli me shor hai, -Rajiv Gandhi Chor hai". Unfortunately, Rajiv Gandhi could not cope with, nor survived that "presumed" scandal. Now his son Rahul himself restores that kind of  foul play against another sitting Prime Minister.  Mr. Modi should have sued him for libel. That is overdue now.

snippet.textDisplay:
There is nothing new about this step and it is being wrongly reported as a consequence of the Pulwama attack. This decision was taken in 2016 following the Uri attack, as confirmed by our own Water Resources ministry. Besides, this water already belongs to India as per the Indus Water Treaty. Allocation of funds for the projects was done in December 2018. The actual stoppage of the water could take upto 6 further years. The quantity of water which will be stopped is about 1.6 million acre feet, which is about 1 per cent of what Pakistan receives (more than that much is let go by Pakistan into the Arabian Sea).
So, in summary, we will stop 1 per cent of the water flowing to Pakistan, which already belonged to us by treaty, six years from now, according to a decision taken two years ago.
P.S. Wow, the anchor and his "national security advisor" are either completely clueless or BJP shills. They kept saying "This govt is not afraid of international pressure." That may or may not be true, but WHY would the international community put pressure on India over this ??? Under the Indus Water Treaty, which was negotiated by the very same international community, the water already belongs to us. It's already ours, why would they care whether we use it or not?

snippet.textDisplay:
No, they are not playing cards or Ludo, Rahul. They are trying to make as much money as they can before they can hand over the state to the governor. All three parties in the Maha Aghadi have only one thing in common-corruption. After the way they have handled the corona emergency, they know for sure that they will not get voted again. So make money while the Father-Son shine. Once the state goes beyond recovery, they will hand it over to the governor so that they can say that it was the governor in power when the state sank in corona. They too, like Sonia Gandhi, tend to think that Indians are still the illiterates that they were during our independence and can be cajoled into voting for them with 500/ notes. Pawar must have by now, destroyed any proofs of his mis-deeds when he was in power just as Ajit Pawar got all the 72000 cr irrigation scandal papers destroyed by fire. Now that they have washed themselves clean of all the corruption they did before, they are free to go. Rahul said that they had been handing over cash to the poor, which means that all the funds have disappeared into their pockets. So what if the Maharastra population goes down in corona? It would have done so anyway because of its "connectivity." They are in power for only one thing and that is not to take responsibility. At one time Maharastra was the best administered state. Today it is a parody of administration. Patients, even of cancer, are left under the fly-over without even proper toilet facilities. Come the rains, I hope Rahul and his Sena have taught them to swim, because the part under the flyovers is generally under 3-4 feet of water.
This Congress spokesperson says trains are not running. Why are they not running? Because Maharastra Govt has not even done the tests of the migrants that are going to UP/MP/Bihar, do not even have to give them tickets, just a list, but that is too much work for the govt. Trains that cover the lists received have been given and will run.He says trains are for Orissa and West Bengal. He does not even know that those trains are the ones NOT running because those states cannot manage the migrants as well as cyclones. He should know how difficult it is to even make lists and he expects the receiving states to make arrangements for these migrants stay in isolation, their food arrangements, and their transfer to other trains going to their homes. Really, if a spokesperson is so uninformed, you can imagine what the govt ministers are like. The only information they have is "where is the money." Ajit Pawar once said that the BJP's middle class tendencies makes it impossible for them to get work from the bureaucracy. Why, Ajitji has not even been able to get them to make LISTS of migrants! As a Maharashtrian, I am ashamed of our govt. Unfortunately, we need it to work and it cannnot. Tragic for us.

snippet.textDisplay: If this is considered bad, what Indira Gandhi did to Field Marshal Manekshaw is worse. How many know that congress stopped his salary from 1971 onwards just because he refused to listen to Indira Gandhi on when to start the war. He also told her not to interfere in how military should be run as he is not interfering in how her government should be run. It was Dr. Abdul Kalam as president of India who ensured that all his dues are cleared after almost 25 years. How come none of our so-called "secular" media came to support this great hero? Instead they all praised Indira Gandhi for the victory and threw the great warrior who won the war into the dustbin of history.

snippet.textDisplay:
A reality of 1971
When Indira Gandhi was the Prime Minister, at that time Field Marshal Manekshaw was the Army Chief, Indira Gandhi ordered him to mount Pakistan…
In response, General Manekshaw said that the troops are ready, but will fight at the appropriate time.
But Indira Gandhi immediately ordered for the ascent ...
But, at the right time, the army climbed the East Pakistan into Bangladesh in just 13 days…
When the appropriate time came, Mr. Manekshaw said to Indira Gandhi ... "I do not interfere in your rule .. In the same way do not interfere in military action" ...
After this, the salary of General Manekshaw ji was stopped from 1971 onwards.
But, this son of Mother Bharati never asked for his salary ...
After 25 years while he was in hospital, one day Mr. A. P.J. Abdul Kalam, went to meet him while on the presidency ...
During the conversation at that time, President Shri Kalam Saheb came to know that the man who fought 5-5 wars for his country, was not paid salary since 1971 ... then he took immediate action and left his remaining Payment of the amount of about 1.3 crore rupees was sent to them… This great Gandhi family did not leave such a brave warrior… It is a shame.
Today is the death anniversary of that great warrior, salutations to him.
Jai Hind Jai India
Publicity department
Vishwa Hindu Parishad District Ghaziabad

snippet.textDisplay:
खबर चल रही है कि एक और व्यवसायी 5000 करोड़ रुपये का बैंक लोन लेकर बिना चुकाए देश छोड़ कर नाइजीरिया भाग चुका है लेकिन शुरुआती आक्रोश के बाद कांग्रेस ने अचानक इस व्यवसायी के मुद्दे को लेकर मोदी पर तंज कसने बंद कर दिए हैं....आपको इसका कारण पता है क्यों? आइये बताता हूँ...

जैसे ही खबर आई कि 5000 करोड़ रुपये लेकर एक और गुजराती व्यवसायी नितिन संदेसरा नाइजीरिया भाग गया है तत्काल कांग्रेस ने कहना प्रारम्भ कर दिया कि एक और व्यवसायी को मोदी ने भगा दिया लेकिन कुछ घंटे के आक्रोश के बाद कांग्रेस शांत हो गयी जिसके कुछ कारण निम्न हैं...

1. कांग्रेस इस मुद्दे पर अब शांत ही रहेगी क्योंकि नितिन संदेसरा अहमद पटेल का बिजनेस पार्टनर है।
2. अहमद पटेल का बेटा और दामाद स्टर्लिंग बायोटेक नाम की इस कंपनी के असली मालिक बताए जाते हैं।
3. कुछ महीने पहले ही कंपनी की चल-अचल संपत्तियां ईडी ने जब्त कर ली हैं। जिसकी वैल्यू करीब 5000 करोड़ रुपये है।
4. 2016 में नोटबंदी के बाद पहली बार पता चला कि इस कंपनी ने आंध्रा बैंक से 5000 करोड़ रुपये ले रखे हैं।
5. नोटबंदी के पहले से नितिन संदेसरा दुबई में रह रहा था। फिर वापस कभी नहीं आया। अब वहां से नाइजीरिया चला गया क्योंकि सरकार दुबई से उसके प्रत्यर्पण की बात कर रही है।
6. इस केस में कंपनी के कई अफसर और आंध्रा बैंक के डायरेक्टर जेल जा चुके हैं।
7. बस अब किसी दिन अहमद पटेल का दामाद और बेटा गिरफ्तार होगा, फिर नैरेटिव बदल जाएगा और कहा जाएगा कि मोदी सरकार बदले की कार्रवाई कर रही है....तो आइये हम कांग्रेस के इस वक्तव्य का इन्तेजार करें

snippet.textDisplay:
शेखचिल्ली को त्यागपत्र देने की कोई इच्छा नहीं थी, पर अपने को महान भी साबित करना था | अतः सोनिआ, प्रियंका, मनमोहन सिंह, रोबर्ट वाड्रा, दिग्विजय, सुरजेवाला, ईत्यादि ने फैसला किया की हार का नकली बकरा बनने का ड्रामा शेखचिल्ली राहुल त्यागपत्र देने की बात से करेगा | हारने का उत्तरदायित्वा अपने मथ्थे लेगा और फिर हम सारे लोग घढ़ियाल के आंसू दिखा कर उसे बचा लेंगे | देखिये सीडब्लूसी मीटिंग में क्या हुआ |

शेखचिल्ली राहुल: मैं पार्टी के प्रधान के पद से त्यागपत्र दूंगा |

सोनिआ: मैं इसका विरोध करती हूँ क्योंकि वह मेंरा बेटा है और इसमें ही मोदी को गंदी गालियां देने का साहस है |

दिग्गी : मैं इसका विरोध करता हूँ क्योंकि जो मैं उसे कहने के लिए कहता हूँ वह अपने भाषण में कह देता है |

प्रियंका वाड्रा: मैं इसका विरोध करती हूँ क्योंकि वह मेंरा भाई है और इसने ही मेरे पति को देश का पैसा लूटने में हमेशा मदद किया

मनमोहन सिंह: मैं इसका विरोध करता हूँ क्योंकि वह बिना मोबाइल फ़ोन देखे कोई फॉर्म नहीं भर सकता |

सुरजेवाला (सूजी): मैं इसका विरोध करता हूँ क्योंकि वह मेरे लिए जनता के मनोरंजन  के लिए सबसे अच्छा माध्यम है |

रोबर्ट वाड्रा : मैं इसका विरोध करता हूँ क्योंकि वह मेरे देश को लूटने में बहुत सहायता करता है | इस शेखचिल्ली के बिना मेरी कंपनी एक दिन में ही डूब जाएगी |

शेखचिल्ली राहुल: ठीक है, मैं आपको निराश नहीं करना चाहता | मैं अपना त्यागपतत्र वापस लेता हूँ |

सोनिआ, प्रियंका, मनमोहन सिंह, रोबर्ट वाड्रा, दिग्विजय, सुरजेवाला, ईत्यादि: आप  महान हैं शेखचिल्ली राहुल| अब आप जा कर जनेवु धारण कर लें |
